# DNS Configuration Guide

## For mydomain.com

### A Records
@ → 76.76.21.21 (Vercel IP)

### CNAME Records
www → cname.vercel-dns.com
*. → cname.vercel-dns.com (Wildcard)

### MX Records (if needed for email)
@ → mail.mydomain.com

### TXT Records
@ → "v=spf1 include:_spf.vercel.net ~all"
_dmarc → "v=DMARC1; p=none; rua=mailto:dmarc@mydomain.com"

## SSL Configuration
Vercel automatically provisions SSL certificates via Let's Encrypt